high_descs: Turn around and walk to the tennis racket on the floor leaning against the desk.
Pick up the tennis racket from the floor.
Turn around and walk in front of the lamp on the small end table.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket by the light of a table lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the closest part of the desk.
Pick up the tennis racket from the floor.
Turn around and walk right to the side table with the lamp on it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a tennis rack by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the edge of the desk near the mirror
Pick up the tennis racket from the ground
Turn around and walk to the small dresser by the door
Turn on the lamp on the dresser
anns.task_desc: Examine the tennis racket by light of the lamp

high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the tennis racket.
Pick up the tennis racket on the floor.
Turn around and walk towards the edge of the bed, then turn left and walk towards the desk with the small green lamp on it.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a tennis racket by the light of a green lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and veer right to the closest short side of the desk.
Pick up the racket from the ground.
Turn around and go ahead and right to the night stand to the right of the door.
Turn on the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Look at a racket by the light of a lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and stand in front of the racket on the floor near the desk.
Pick the racket up from the floor.
Go left and then left again to face the small table with the lamp on it.
Turn the lamp on.
anns.task_desc: Hold a racket and turn a lamp on.
